{"tid":844650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先比人抽水！","createTime":"2018-10-02T04:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T05:13:47.000Z","uid":213661,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a110f5fc8d623eb1772dd0f5c9fe53bc15c506d0","tid":844650,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"頭先係荃灣個邊搭𨋢，明明成部得2個人，計埋我得3個，個男人企正係門口，兩隻手臂擘得特別開。<br />\n<br />\n一開頭我以為係啲老mk鍾意咁企覺得霸氣啲。但屌你老母愈黎愈唔對路，做乜撚野佢隻手係咁hi鳩我，又感覺到佢一直擰轉頭望實我。<br />\n<br />\n我縮埋左好幾次，佢隻手就擘開得越大黎掂我。最撚痛苦係佢個身好撚臭腐爛味。 臨開門仲問我去邊，我答左佢番工。就雞咁腳走，點知佢一路跟住我去到公司樓下，再問我洗唔洗陪我，咁岩我拎起電話打比老細，佢可能以為我報警就轉身走左。<br />\n<br />\n本身都唔會對啲基佬反感，但經過今次我宣佈所有死基佬比人歧視都係唔抵可憐。"},{"pid":"c2aaf43623d349e88a6a4ec584d89d4c46695200","tid":844650,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:48:17.000Z","msg":"搞基=愛滋病人"},{"pid":"ca0e8fcc8f8b650ac8eedad51ef3421d28384429","tid":844650,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"巴打我又係荃灣 今晚收工等我保護你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22d23279a4bd4a355b5ef3d11bd1991dfa424d6","tid":844650,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0e8fcc8f8b650ac8eedad51ef3421d28384429","tid":844650,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"巴打我又係荃灣 今晚收工等我保護你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"你一定都係基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d51644a1dab63a7d23113958f8e04e90dd293cf","tid":844650,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9ae4fdf7559af2e7fb4a31977f8aa6dffafb1bb","tid":844650,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22d23279a4bd4a355b5ef3d11bd1991dfa424d6","tid":844650,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0e8fcc